occupation: Protector of Xarth Three and Council Deputy of the Uuchan Delegation
significantissues: Opposed the Guardians of the Galaxy in their attempts to stop the Skrull invasion of Knowhere and fought against Cosmo and the Guardians because of a gross misunderstanding (Guardians of the Galaxy #4-6, 2008)
